data.description: This stunning four-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bath home has an open-concept living area perfect for entertaining, with plenty of natural light, new paint, and new carpet! The spacious kitchen features SS appliances and ample storage space. The primary suite is a true retreat, with a large walk-in closet, a luxurious en-suite bathroom with a large tub, and a separate shower. Three additional bedrooms offer plenty of room for all! Outside, the large backyard is perfect for summer barbecues or relaxing in the sun. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home is just minutes from shopping, dining, schools, post, and entertainment. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful house your new home! NEW HVAC as well.
